# Project Images Directory

Place project screenshots and images here.

## Structure
Each project should have its own folder:
```
projects/
├── wifi-csi/
│   ├── hero.jpg
│   ├── screenshot-1.jpg
│   └── screenshot-2.jpg
├── tinylinux/
│   └── hero.jpg
└── thumbnails/
    ├── wifi-csi-thumb.jpg
    └── tinylinux-thumb.jpg
```

## Naming Convention
- Hero images: `hero.jpg`
- Screenshots: `screenshot-[number].jpg`
- Thumbnails: `[project-slug]-thumb.jpg`

## Recommended Specs
- Hero: 1200x630px (16:9 ratio)
- Screenshots: 1920x1080px
- Thumbnails: 400x300px
- Format: JPEG or WebP
